        "subject": "LU-154 Prototype of d_compare has changed in 2.6.38",
        "message": "LU-154 Prototype of d_compare has changed in 2.6.38\n\nThe prototype of ->d_compare has changed in 2.6.38. See the kernel commit for more information.\nhttp://git.kernel.org/?p=linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux-2.6.git;a=commit;h=621e155a3591962420eacdd39f6f0aa29ceb221e\nThe good news is that starting 2.6.38, ll_dcompare() no longer relies on the name to be inlined in the dentry.\n\nChange-Id: Iacdf9c1d3134af05b5ad8da858472d37880d06ff\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
